  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_4_4882-4903",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4882-4903",
      "markText": "一个人，总有个嗜好，没有嗜好，那是木头了。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4882&rangeEnd=4903",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4882&rangeEnd=4903"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_4_438-508",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "438-508",
      "markText": "四川的天气，最是变幻莫测，一晴可以二三十天。当中秋节前后，大太阳熏蒸了一个季节，由两三场雷雨，变成了连绵的阴雨，一天跟着一天，只管向下沉落。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=438&rangeEnd=508",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=438&rangeEnd=508"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_4_1136-1152",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1136-1152",
      "markText": "君问归期未有期，巴山夜雨涨秋池。",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1136&rangeEnd=1152",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1136&rangeEnd=1152"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_4_2532-2601",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2532-2601",
      "markText": "。国际问题，只有各国的首脑人物自己可以知道自己的事。就是对手方面的态度，他也摸不着。中国那些国际问题专家，那种佛庙抽签式的预言，千万信不得",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2532&rangeEnd=2601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2532&rangeEnd=2601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_30_27613-27690",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "27613-27690",
      "markText": "此外是黑茫茫的，什么也看不见。各家都有人站在屋檐下，听候二次警报，用耳代目，像死人似地等着。鸡犬无声，也不知到了什么时候。只觉得是长夜漫漫的，长夜漫漫的。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=27613&rangeEnd=27690",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=30&rangeStart=27613&rangeEnd=27690"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_11_6599-6646",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6599-6646",
      "markText": "。人也是这样，永远是父母保护孩子，孩子大了，并不怎样保护父母。可是他自己有孩子，他又得保护了。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6599&rangeEnd=6646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6599&rangeEnd=6646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_5_6588-6643",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6588-6643",
      "markText": "正说着，有一位白太太含着笑由身边过去。李先生暗下叫一声不好。因为这位白夫人，也是太太的牌友，她们是很有帮助的。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6588&rangeEnd=6643",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6588&rangeEnd=6643"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_4_6413-6431",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6413-6431",
      "markText": "土洋火咯，庞臭！你还是在灯上点吧。”",
      "totalCount": 110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23303893&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6413&rangeEnd=6431",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/738322f0716396d57385480?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6413&rangeEnd=6431"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23303893_5_1115-1175",
